c: 18
v: 21
t: "Thus did We inform the people about them that they may know the promise of God is true, and there is no doubt that the Hour will come. As they were arguing among themselves as to what should be done with them, (some) said: \"Erect a monument over them. Their Lord is best cognisant of them.\" Those who prevailed, said: \"We shall build a place of worship over their (sepulchre)"